OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe mix of
OL,6,Fclear spells and blustery showers will
OL,7,Fcontinue through the night. The strong
OL,8,Fsoutheasterly wind and coastal gales
OL,9,Fwill decrease, turning fresh south to
OL,10,Fsouthwesterly towards the morning.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FAny showers will soon clear
OL,13,Fduring the morning to leave increasing
OL,14,Fsunny spells. A few showers may affect
OL,15,FOrkney in the afternoon, staying dry
OL,16,Fand sunny over Shetland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
