OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,6,Fwith sunny periods Tuesday. Cloud and
OL,7,Frain spread northeast Wednesday,
OL,8,Fclearing north Wednesday night. Bright
OL,9,Fspells and showers follow from the
OL,10,Fsouth Thursday. Windy at times
OL,11,FWednesday and Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
